[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

1544
01:02:01,000 --> 01:02:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite je glupo dole te.

1545
01:02:02,000 --> 01:02:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Toliko se propagirate je neki zdrav način života?

1546
01:02:05,000 --> 01:02:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo ode.

1547
01:02:06,000 --> 01:02:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zeleni čaj, čija, sveveće, vegetarijanske.

1548
01:02:10,000 --> 01:02:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne samo to.

1549
01:02:11,000 --> 01:02:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odlasak u prirodu.

1550
01:02:12,000 --> 01:02:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] A idemo na šumjama.

1551
01:02:14,000 --> 01:02:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1552
01:02:15,000 --> 01:02:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo ubiti krave ili kušta vjetra.

1553
01:02:17,000 --> 01:02:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bila na filozofskom kafeu.

1554
01:02:22,000 --> 01:02:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tema je bila uzicaj medija na mišljenje publika.

1555
01:02:27,000 --> 01:02:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] I meni žena kaže, mrtva hladna, joj znate ima puno krava i krava ima jako izvode mesanj.

1556
01:02:34,000 --> 01:02:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] To sam odustala.

1557
01:02:36,000 --> 01:02:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su iracionalni.

1558
01:02:40,000 --> 01:02:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, u ekonomiji, kad dođe se na ekonomske fabute, propagira se činjenica da su ljudi jako dobri.

1559
01:02:47,000 --> 01:02:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vrlo će brzo to onako...

1560
01:02:50,000 --> 01:02:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve će se srediti.

1561
01:02:52,000 --> 01:02:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Edimo ova ruka, ono...

1562
01:02:54,000 --> 01:02:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidve ruka.

1563
01:02:56,000 --> 01:02:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj...

1564
01:02:59,000 --> 01:03:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] A u politologiji polazimo činjenica od Hobbesa.

1565
01:03:02,000 --> 01:03:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, da su ljudi iracionalni.

1566
01:03:05,000 --> 01:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] I vode se isključio vlastnim interesima.

1567
01:03:08,000 --> 01:03:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ih je dobro manipulirati.

1568
01:03:11,000 --> 01:03:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer znajte vidjeti njihovo sreći korak.

1569
01:03:14,000 --> 01:03:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Interes, interes, interes, interes.

1570
01:03:16,000 --> 01:03:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] I što je još bilo?

1571
01:03:18,000 --> 01:03:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Daj se te papire malo.

1572
01:03:21,000 --> 01:03:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, bilo je, furamo se na zajednu tranziciju, se više, više, avti.

1573
01:03:25,000 --> 01:03:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ušumiljavamo se, ubijamo krave.

1574
01:03:28,000 --> 01:03:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, nemoj to mi na živci.

1575
01:03:31,000 --> 01:03:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovako infrastruktura, Zagreba...

1576
01:03:33,000 --> 01:03:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaj će li se preti prudog, velikog Odise, kaj će rekli?

1577
01:03:37,000 --> 01:03:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

1578
01:03:38,000 --> 01:03:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu da ovi složiti tu, znači da se sve ovećava.

1579
01:03:41,000 --> 01:03:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Strašno, strašno, strašno, da.

1580
01:03:43,000 --> 01:03:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] A pravo ću gospoda Tomašovića dobiti.

1581
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moje da pitam?

1582
01:03:47,000 --> 01:03:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moje da pitam?

1583
01:03:49,000 --> 01:03:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moje da pitam?

1584
01:03:50,000 --> 01:03:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi katežimo kam...

1585
01:03:55,000 --> 01:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neh samo dođemo.

1586
01:03:57,000 --> 01:03:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zelenoj tranziciji.

1587
01:03:58,000 --> 01:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ej, kuma da ratea.

1588
01:04:02,000 --> 01:04:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moram.

1589
01:04:04,000 --> 01:04:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na kraju svega.

1590
01:04:05,000 --> 01:04:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju svega.

1591
01:04:06,000 --> 01:04:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Osim što se baviš trbuškom plesom.

1592
01:04:08,000 --> 01:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] E, okej.

1593
01:04:09,000 --> 01:04:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1594
01:04:10,000 --> 01:04:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Daj neku poruku, nade, posetire, daj nešto.

1595
01:04:13,000 --> 01:04:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da...

1596
01:04:15,000 --> 01:04:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti sam prva čušta i skuma.

1597
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam prva čušta i skuma.

1598
01:04:19,000 --> 01:04:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo.

1599
01:04:20,000 --> 01:04:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imam pravno da rekla.

1600
01:04:21,000 --> 01:04:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

1601
01:04:22,000 --> 01:04:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ispora od letušku navoda.

1602
01:04:23,000 --> 01:04:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dum.

1603
01:04:24,000 --> 01:04:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dum, dum.

1604
01:04:25,000 --> 01:04:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ale, opomena.

1605
01:04:26,000 --> 01:04:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako.

1606
01:04:27,000 --> 01:04:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam danas upoznala od rame u jednu ženu.

1607
01:04:31,000 --> 01:04:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je bila po meni u jako lošim stanju.

1608
01:04:34,000 --> 01:04:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam je prišla i pitala sam je dobro što je bilo.

1609
01:04:39,000 --> 01:04:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže ona meni da ne znam se znaći u gradu.

1610
01:04:42,000 --> 01:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ju povela sa sobom.

1611
01:04:45,000 --> 01:04:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ona je rekla meni da je ona zapravo jako loša.

1612
01:04:49,000 --> 01:04:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam vidjela na njoj da je loša.

1613
01:04:52,000 --> 01:04:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] I krenuli smo neki razgovor.

1614
01:04:54,000 --> 01:04:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ju zagrlila i ona se krenula plakati.

1615
01:04:57,000 --> 01:04:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam da rekla ti moj broj.

1616
01:04:59,000 --> 01:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se oz nešto zapne zove mene.

1617
01:05:01,000 --> 01:05:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] I s tim bi završila kogod smo mi izmanipulirani.

1618
01:05:05,000 --> 01:05:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jadni nekad.

1619
01:05:08,000 --> 01:05:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Utopini u svojim brigama.

1620
01:05:11,000 --> 01:05:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne čitamo.

1621
01:05:13,000 --> 01:05:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek se na sebi može raditi.

1622
01:05:15,000 --> 01:05:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] A nikada se ne radi o sebi.

1623
01:05:17,000 --> 01:05:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ima još dobrih ljudi na svijetu.

1624
01:05:21,000 --> 01:05:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima.

1625
01:05:22,000 --> 01:05:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam zavirla tu ženu i ta žena se razplakala.

1626
01:05:25,000 --> 01:05:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna od njih je naša kuma.

1627
01:05:27,000 --> 01:05:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji zapratite na društvenim mrežama.

1628
01:05:29,000 --> 01:05:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zapratite naši podcast.

1629
01:05:30,000 --> 01:05:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čušpa i se.

1630
01:05:31,000 --> 01:05:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pretplatite se.

1631
01:05:32,000 --> 01:05:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nama ne treba je vaše pare.

1632
01:05:33,000 --> 01:05:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nama treba je vaše skranje.

1633
01:05:35,000 --> 01:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, ekipa.

1634
01:05:37,000 --> 01:05:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala, vidimo se.

1635
01:05:38,000 --> 01:05:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog.

1636
01:05:39,000 --> 01:05:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo se.

1637
01:05:40,000 --> 01:05:43,280
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite kanal.

